OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDiscounts for off-peak     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Felectricity use raised     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The value of discounts on electricity  
OL,6, bills for households that cut peak-time
OL,7, use is to be raised, National Grid ESO 
OL,8, has said.                              
OL,10,FHouseholds will be paid #3 per kilowatt
OL,11,Fhour instead of 52p, if they avoid     
OL,12,Fhigh-power activities, such as cooking,
OL,13,Fwhen demand is high, the firm said.    
OL,15,FEnergy firms Octopus and E.On had said 
OL,16,Fthe 52p payment to incentivise         
OL,17,Fcustomers to sign up was too low.      
OL,19,FThe scheme is aimed at easing pressure 
OL,20,Fon UK power grids this winter.         
